messageBody:
Hi all,

I've been working on the Unicode proposal and I've put what I've got so
far in the Files section under Unicode Proposal.
Anyone who wants to make any additions/changes, post them in this thread
and I'll merge them.

Also I've half completed and uploaded form n3102 which is the form which
is the summery for all Unicode proposals.
It gives a good overview of what needs to be in a proposal.
